<package>
  <metadata>
    <id>HBD.Configuration</id>
    <version>${NugetVersion}</version>
    <title>HBD.Configuration</title>
    <authors>Duy Hoang</authors>
    <owners>Duy Hoang</owners>
    <description>
      This is a service that allows loading the configuration from various sources.
      The ConfigurationService will cache the configuration in the Cache service for the subsequence use.
      Once the source config has changed, or the cache expired then the service will call the Adapter again to reload the latest version of config.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>
      Version ${NugetVersion}
      - Added Configuration Service allows to load and caches the config info from a file, database, and any other storage.
      - Added the Json adapter to read the information from the json file.
    </releaseNotes>
